
### Sample `.gitignore` for a Flask Application

```plaintext
# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# Environment variables
.env
*.env

# Flask instance folder
instance/

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
ENV/
.venv/
.env/

# IDE and editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
*.log

# Database files
*.sqlite3
*.db

# Coverage reports
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Pytest cache
.cache

# Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Miscellaneous
*.DS_Store
*.egg-info/
*.egg
```
